        Initiates a new Fractal tree.
        Parameters:
        leafWidth - the width of the leaves.
        leafHeight - the height of the leaves.
        leafDensity - the density of the leaves.
        branchMinLength - the minimum length of branches.
        branchMaxLength - the maximum length of branches.
        stemLength - the length of the trees stem.
